---
import LongformPageLayout from '../../layouts/LongformPageLayout.astro';
import ParkedSection from '../../components/ParkedSection.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../../config';
---

{siteConfig.sections.projects ? (
  <LongformPageLayout
    title="Projects"
    intro="A selected set of things I have built across product engineering, internal tools, and personal experiments."
  >
    <h2>MAIA: AI Sales Coordinator</h2>

    <p>
      A dashboard integrating with various data sources to visualize core startup metrics.
      It improved data transparency across non-technical teams and reduced ad-hoc data requests by 40%.
    </p>

    <h2>NutriTrack AI</h2>

    <p>
      Built to scratch my own itch for a nutrition tracking application that does not rely on the cloud.
      It focuses heavily on keyboard navigation and sub-10ms response times for all rendering.
      The source is on <a href="https://github.com/hoguanting/NutriTrack-AI">GitHub</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Fidemo: AI-Powered Frame Interpolation</h2>

    <p>
      Built to scratch my own itch for a frame interpolation application that does not rely on the cloud.
      It focuses heavily on keyboard navigation and sub-10ms response times for all rendering.
      The source is on <a href="https://github.com/hoguanting/NutriTrack-AI">GitHub</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>TeaMWork 2024</h2>

    <p>
      I joined <a href="https://www.bdo.my/">BDO</a> as an intern in 2024 to work on this project. I collaborated with a team of 6 students from <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/monash-warwick-alliance/posts/?feedView=all">Monash Warwick Alliance</a> to develop a CSR gamification platform for BDO internal use. We conducted a comprehensive analysis and stakeholder requirements studies for internal CSR platform redesign. We designed a new gamified user experience by researching competing platforms and creating a low-fidelity prototype in Figma. We defined the project's technical scope, roadmap, and budget for the new wellness-focused gamified platform, presenting the final feasibility report and technical specifications to BDO management. Source available on <a href="https://github.com/hoguanting/ThoughFull-CSR-Gamification">GitHub</a>.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <p>My other mini projects, all collected on <a href="https://github.com/hoguanting">GitHub</a>:</p>

    <ul class="project-link-list">
      <li><a href="https://github.com/hoguanting/Static-Factory-Game" class="project-list-link">Static Factory Game</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/hoguanting/FlappyBirb" class="project-list-link">Flappy Birb</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/hoguanting/haskell-bnf-parser-generator" class="project-list-link">BNF Parser Generator</a></li>
    </ul>
  </LongformPageLayout>
) : (
  <ParkedSection title="Projects" />
)}
